  "body": "## Feature Request\r\n\r\n**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe:**\r\nWhen TiKV calculating `block-cache-size`, it uses `/proc/meminfo` to get total memory. Unfortunately \r\n/proc/meminfo, /proc/vmstat and friends are not containerized. Meaning that they are not cgroup-aware. So for docker with limited memory resource, TiKV may set a too large block cache size and easy to OOM.\r\n\r\n**Describe the feature you'd like:**\r\nmaybe we can check `cat /sys/fs/group/memory/memory.limit_in_bytes` to make it cgroup-aware",
